# 🧠 AI Virtual Character System – LoRA Models, Fine-Tuned Checkpoints & Prompt Engineering

Welcome to my generative AI showcase. This repository includes **LoRA adapters**, **fine-tuned models**, and **prompt engineering frameworks** developed to support virtual characters across **games, storytelling platforms, and immersive environments**.

---

## 🎯 Objective

To build a scalable framework of **AI-driven characters** that combines:

- 🎨 Visual Generation (Stable Diffusion, LoRAs)
- 🧠 Dialogue/NLP (Transformer models)
- 🧪 Real-time Prompt Engineering
- 🌐 Web/API Deployment (Flask, Gradio)

---

